The paper also discusses neural network architectures, which suggests that it may fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions denoising, which is a common problem in neural networks and could place it under neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper discusses techniques for preserving large-scale structure, which could also place it under multimedia (cs.MM).
